Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Indiana:
1 SECTION 1. IC 25-23-1-3, AS AMENDED BY P.L.148-2023,
2 SECTION 12, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
3 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 3. At any time there is a vacancy or expiration of
4 a term, the Indiana State Nurses Association shall recommend to the
5 governor a list of qualified nurses for appointment to the board in the
6 number of not less than twice the number of:
7 (1) nurse vacancies to be filled; or
8 (2) nurse appointments to be made.
